import React from "react"; import "./InfoEdgeSection.css"; export default function InfoEdgeSection() { return (

We Are Supported by

Seva UK –

Provided the spacious, well-equipped premises where our children learn and grow./n

Hiten Fasteners Pvt. Ltd. and 4G5G Consultant Pvt. Ltd. –

Our backbone partners, supporting us consistently through CSR funds./n

Bank of Baroda –

Donated physiotherapy beds to aid in children’s therapy sessions./n

International Medical Association –

Provided parallel bars, helping children walk with the aid of calipers.

Rotary Club –

Donated a stepping frame, enabling children to train in climbing steps.

We Are Associated with clubs

Lions Club –

Supplied uniforms for our children.

Johnson Lifts Co. –

Donated and installed a lift, making our school building accessible to all.

Canara Bank –

Provided a ball tub to help children improve their balance.

Local Donors –

Offering constant moral encouragement and financial support that keeps our mission alive.
